        "cooked": "<p>Of cause, the performance will be lower.</p>\n<p>If it is not acceptable, you may duplicate data and insert two pairs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>{uuid, {name, address}}</li>\n<li>{name+uuid, address}</li>\n</ul>",
